title Observer

skinparam legendBackgroundColor #f9f9f9
skinparam legendBorderColor #999999

legend right
**Intent**: One-to-many dependency; notify dependents automatically on state change.

**Use when**: Event systems, GUI, reactive updates.

**Key participants**: Subject, Observer, ConcreteSubject, ConcreteObserver.
endlegend

interface Observer {
  +update(subject: Subject)
}

class ConcreteObserverA
class ConcreteObserverB

interface Subject {
  +attach(obs: Observer)
  +detach(obs: Observer)
  +notifyObservers()
}

class ConcreteSubject {
  -state
}

Observer <|.. ConcreteObserverA
Observer <|.. ConcreteObserverB

Subject <|.. ConcreteSubject
ConcreteSubject o-- Observer : observers
@enduml